'''胃灼熱'''（{{lang-en|'''heartburn'''}}），亦稱為"酸消化不良"('''acid indigestion''')<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/ger-and-gerd-in-adults/Pages/overview.aspx | title=Gastroesophageal Reflux (GER) and Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease (GERD) in Adults | format= | work=The National Institute of Diabetes and Digestive and Kidney Diseases | accessdate=2015-07-24 | archive-date=2015-07-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725032223/http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/ger-and-gerd-in-adults/Pages/overview.aspx | dead-url=no }}</ref> 是指在中[[胸|胸部]]或[[epigastrium|上中腹部]](epigastrium)所產生的灼熱感。<ref>{{DorlandsDict|four/000047500|heartburn}}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite book |title=Differential diagnosis in primary care |publisher=Wolters Kluwer Health/Lippincott Williams & Wilkins |location=Philadelphia |year=2008 |pages=211 |isbn=0-7817-6812-8 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/medical/pyrosis|title=Pyrosis Medical Definition - Merriam-Webster Medical Dictionary|work=merriam-webster.com|accessdate=24 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725013215/http://www.merriam-webster.com/medical/pyrosis|dead-url=no}}</ref>疼痛往往源於胸部且可放射到頸部，喉部，或下頜角。

胃灼熱通常是由於[[胃酸|胃酸]]返流（胃反流）進入食管而且是[[GERD|胃食管反流疾病]]（GERD）的主要症狀。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.nlm.nih.gov/cgi/mesh/2005/MB_cgi?mode&term=heartburn | title=Heartburn | work=National Library of Medicine | accessdate=2015-07-24 | archive-date=2016-03-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312161013/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/cgi/mesh/2005/MB_cgi?mode&term=heartburn | dead-url=no }}</ref>約有 0.6％ 的案例是屬於[[冠狀動脈疾病|冠狀動脈疾病]]的症狀。<ref name=Cardiac09>{{cite journal |vauthors=Kato H, Ishii T, Akimoto T, Urita Y, Sugimoto M |title=Prevalence of linked angina and gastroesophageal reflux disease in general practice |journal=World J. Gastroenterol. |volume=15 |issue=14 |pages=1764–8 |date=April 2009 |pmid=19360921 |pmc=2668783 |doi= 10.3748/wjg.15.1764|url=}}</ref>

==定義==
[[消化不良|消化不良]]這個術語指包括胃灼熱及許多其他的症狀。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Duvnjak|first1=edited by Marko|title=Dyspepsia in clinical practice|date=2011|publisher=Springer|location=New York|isbn=9781441917300|page=2|edition=1. Aufl.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=UGpATfS5-T8C&pg=PA2|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413173111/https://books.google.ca/books?id=UGpATfS5-T8C&pg=PA2|dead-url=no}}</ref> 消化不良有時被定義為[[腹痛|心口痛]]與胃灼熱的複合症狀。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Delaney B, Ford AC, Forman D, Moayyedi P, Qume M |title=Initial management strategies for dyspepsia |journal=Cochrane Database Syst Rev |volume= |issue=4 |pages=CD001961 |year=2005 |pmid=16235292 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD001961.pub2 |url= |editor1-last=Delaney |editor1-first=Brendan}}</ref>胃灼熱通常可與[[胃食管反流病|胃食管反流病]]交互使用表示同一症狀，而不是僅僅在描述一個人的胸部灼熱症狀。<ref>{{cite book |author1=Sajatovic, Martha |author2=Loue, Sana |author3=Koroukian, Siran M. |title=Encyclopedia of aging and public health |url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaagin00loue |publisher=Springer |location=Berlin |year=2008 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaagin00loue/page/n435 419] |isbn=0-387-33753-9 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>

